{"tid":2276780,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺個市已經開始左牛一（牛市一期）？？？","createTime":"2020-11-08T04:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T05:25:21.000Z","uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"368d07a9e95efc39633afa3c67bfee43c74a8fd6","tid":2276780,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"在上升週期出現時，<strong><span class=\"red\">通常是經濟處於不景氣的時候</span></strong>。這時，股市低迷，但開始有反彈跡象，正是入市時機，稱為牛市一期。<br />\n<br />\n另外，2016年起基本上是板塊輪流炒，炒完科網，跟著是汽車、內房、內險及內銀，不少板塊均有理想表現，因為資金充裕，這亦是典型牛一特徵。<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/blog/zh/牛一-牛二定牛三-拆解牛熊不同週期特徵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyhero.com.hk%2Fblog%2Fzh%2F%E7%89%9B%E4%B8%80-%E7%89%9B%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%9A%E7%89%9B%E4%B8%89-%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%89%9B%E7%86%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%9F%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%B5&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft27tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=00d81b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/blog/zh/牛一-牛二定牛三-拆解牛熊不同週期特徵</a></span><br />\n<br />\n中晒，依家咪就係肺炎令到經濟不景 <br />\n但你feel 到個市開始反彈，<br />\n又不斷炒完新經濟股，又炒返舊經濟<br />\n<br />\n唔通真係「牛一」？？？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445e433ecacaf98bf6983f6e58011ea52d6f17af","tid":2276780,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"495a85ef36e8307489494cd475b2d751933ab8e1","tid":2276780,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"係牛二"},{"pid":"0bd20d6561a0506d5dcb046fabd0e6b5b11b71d9","tid":2276780,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495a85ef36e8307489494cd475b2d751933ab8e1","tid":2276780,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"係牛二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2